msgid "The majority of Kolab Systems employees is, and has been for a long time, intimately familiar with the Fedora Project in participatory fashion, and at leadership levels."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/introduction/what-is-the-recommended-distribution.rst:156
# 01d21a242260478eb4df12a611fe8f3a
msgid "The majority of system engineers employed by Kolab Systems is RHCE certified."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/introduction/what-is-the-recommended-distribution.rst:159
